description: The Beer Style skill gives the user information about the different beer styles recognized by the industry. It can give you a short description of the style, what the alcohol content content can be and what the country of origin is.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Beer Style can you describe a Cream Ale
Alexa, ask Beer Style can you tell me how much alcohol is in an American Stout
Alexa, ask Beer Style where is a dark mild from
name: Beer Style
shortDescription: Gives the user basic information about different styles of beer. Short descriptions, alcohol levels and countries of origin.
